    <div class="span7">
      <h2>Government services. Made Simple.</h2>
      <p>GSAgility was started to make services procurement simple, easy, and FAST.  Our goal is to enable government purchasers to respond quickly to the needs of their agency and the needs of citizens by providing a platform to ask for services.
      <p>Our web-based marketplace will allow government users to post micro-opportunities that independent vendors can bid on to deliver.  No complicated RFPs. No complicated response process for vendors.</p>
      <p>Government gets what it needs, FAST and pays with a purchase card.  Vendors get access to a huge market, and bid on what they want.</p>
      <h5><a href="/forgovernment">Information for Government Purchasers</a></h5>
